Use snapshot of fresh Windows Server 2025 OS (before domain creation and promoting to DC). (Base Win Server)

For MAC address policy select Generate new MAC addresses for all network adapters. Also select Full Clone.

So here we are:

![Windows Server VM Settings](../general-steps//images_ignore/scr16.PNG)

Change NAT network adapter to AD Project in virtual box gui.

Start and log in into SRV01 VM.

```
PS C:\WINDOWS\system32> New-NetIPAddress -InterfaceAlias "Ethernet" -IPAddress 192.168.0.9 -PrefixLength 24 -DefaultGateway 192.168.0.1
PS C:\WINDOWS\system32> Set-DnsClientServerAddress -InterfaceAlias "Ethernet" -ServerAddresses 192.168.0.5
PS C:\WINDOWS\system32> Rename-Computer -NewName "SRV01" -Restart
```

Join in to domain.
```PS C:\WINDOWS\system32> Add-Computer -DomainName "massivedynamic.local" -Credential MASSIVEDYNAMIC\Administrator -Restart```


